assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: iFAST Corporation Ltd. provides investment products and services in Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, China, and India. It operates through Business-to-Business (B2B), Business-to-Consumer (B2C), and Business-to-Business-to-Consumer (B2B2C) divisions. The company's B2B division operates iFAST Central that includes a range of services, including investment products, fee collection, operational support, IT solutions, and wrap account services; iFAST Global Prestige; iFAST pensions that deliver tax-effective employee benefits solutions to companies that want to administer pension schemes for their employees via a digital platform; iFAST Global Markets that provides adviser-assisted wealth management plans; and iFAST ePension, which include pension administrative services and white labeled solutions for scheme sponsors, trustees, and other institutions. Its B2C division provides a distribution and transactional platform to investors through Fundsupermart.com (FSM)/FSMOne website, such as investment products, fee structure, tools to compare investments, customer services support, and research advice products. In addition, the company operates a B2B2C division, which offers fintech solutions, including iFAST API, customized B2B2C, white-label robo-advisory, and bespoke fintech solutions. Further, the company operates bondsupermart.com, a regional bond information portal for investors and wealth advisers; iFAST fund management investment products solutions; and iFAST TV, an investment-focused digital video channel. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Singapore.
